CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 30, 2010

[Cite as 04/30/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-1897.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2003-1865 and 2006-1261. Disciplinary Counsel v. Young.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by respondent, James Cornell Young, of a petition for reinstatement. On April 23, 2010, counsel for respondent, Michael E. Murman, filed a motion for leave to withdraw as counsel.

It is ordered by this court that the motion is granted.

Pfeifer, Acting C. J.
